      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Honest, affordable transportation with real potential. This vehicle is best suited for a budget-minded buyer, commuter backup, or someone looking for a practical project. It offers solid value for the money and a straightforward opportunity to get into a vehicle at an accessible price point. Presented transparently and priced to sell, this is a sensible option for anyone who understands how to spot value where it counts.",
