      "description": "Honest, affordable car that\u2019s perfect for someone looking for cheap, practical transportation without the big upfront cost. It\u2019s not a showroom piece, but it\u2019s a solid little runaround with plenty of life left for the right buyer. Great option for a first car, spare vehicle, or budget commuter. Priced to sell and represented straight \u2014 come have a look and see if it\u2019s the right fit for you.",
