      "description": "Clean, straightforward driver/project with a strong-running powertrain and solid fundamentals. Engine pulls well, transmission engages as it should, and the chassis feels planted with predictable road manners. Not a show car and it has cosmetic wear consistent with age, but it presents as an honest, usable car with good bones for someone who wants affordable transportation or a platform to sort and improve. A smart buy for an enthusiast who values mechanical integrity over cosmetics.",
