      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character that turns heads with its story rather than its polish. It\u2019s an ideal find for someone who sees possibility where others see a blank canvas\u2014a dependable companion for a hands-on owner, a practical runabout, or the start of a rewarding project. There\u2019s charm in its presence, grit in its stance, and plenty of opportunity for the next chapter to be written by you.",
