    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Reliable transportation at an affordable price. This vehicle is being offered as a practical, budget-conscious option for a buyer who wants dependable basic mobility and strong value for the money. It shows its age and is best suited for someone comfortable with an older vehicle, but it remains a straightforward opportunity to get on the road for far less than the cost of newer alternatives. Priced to reflect condition while still representing solid value.",
