    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great budget-friendly option for someone who wants basic transport, a handy runabout, or a project to tinker with. Honest car with character, priced to sell, and a chance to get into something without spending a fortune. If you\u2019re after cheap motoring and don\u2019t mind giving it a bit of TLC, this could be a really worthwhile buy.",
